{
  "comment": "Per-scenario regression thresholds for tests/Aws2Azure.PerfTests. Numbers reflect emulator-bound baselines captured on the project's reference dev hardware; see docs/perf/baseline-latest.md for the live observed snapshot. Operators bump these values manually when a deliberate change to the proxy raises or lowers expected throughput. minThroughputPerSec floors observed ops/s; maxP99Ms ceilings observed p99. Either field can be 0 to opt out of that half of the gate, but EVERY scenario must have an entry — KnownPerfScenariosTests asserts coverage so newly added scenarios force the operator to think about a threshold (use {0,0} to defer if needed).",
